data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the picturesque Glen Lakes community. Nestled within a secure gated enclave, this immaculate 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and tranquil living. Step inside, and you'll be instantly impressed by the open-concept living space, bathed in natural light from large windows that frame views of the lakes. The living room is perfect for hosting guests or relaxing with family, featuring a cozy fireplace for those chilly nights.
